kubectl run pod-name --image=nginx:latest --restart=Never -> To create the pod

kubectl expose pod pod-name --port=80 --target-port=80 --type=LoadBalancer -> To expose the pod

kubectl create deployment deployment-name --image=nginx:latest -> To create the deployment

kubectl expose deployment deployment-name --port=80 --target-port=80 --type=LoadBalancer -> To expose the deployment

kubectl set image deployment/deployment-name container-name=image-name -> To update the deployment

kubectl rollout undo deployment/deployment-name -> To rollback the deployment

kubectl scale deployment deployment-name --replicas=10 -> To scale the deployment
